OL,3,CVictim of murder plot GP says he will
OL,4,C'never get over the anxiety and pain'
OL,6,FA grandfather injected with poison by
OL,7,Fhis partner's GP son over money says
OL,8,Fhe will "never get over the anxiety
OL,9,Fand pain" caused to him and his family.
OL,11,FPatrick O'Hara, 72, was the victim of
OL,12,Fan elaborate murder plot by Dr Thomas
OL,13,FKwan, who disguised himself as a
OL,14,Fcommunity nurse delivering a Covid
OL,15,Fbooster at the Newcastle home of his
OL,16,Fown mother.
OL,18,FMarried father-of-one Kwan, 53,
OL,19,Fadmitted attempted murder on the
OL,20,Fsecond day of a trial earlier this
OL,21,Fmonth at Newcastle Crown Court.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/20
