OL,6,FThe prosecution made the case at the
OL,7,Fsame court on Thursday (17 October)
OL,8,Fthat the crime meets the criteria for
OL,9,Fa whole life sentence which could see
OL,10,Fhim jailed for 35 years.
OL,12,FAt a sentencing hearing, Mr O'Hara
OL,13,Fheld back tears as he told the court
OL,14,Fhis life "completely changed forever"
OL,15,Fat the hands of his former partner's
OL,16,Fson.
