OL,3,CVictim of murder plot GP says he will
OL,4,C'never get over the anxiety and pain'
OL,6,FReading a victim impact statement, he
OL,7,Fsaid: "I genuinely feel as if I have
OL,8,Fbeen to hell and back. Thomas will
OL,9,Fnever comprehend or know what it's
OL,10,Flike to suffer in the manner of which
OL,11,FI am."
OL,13,FHe continued: "I genuinely believe
OL,14,Fthat from his perspective, he only
OL,15,Fwished for his actions to impact one
OL,16,Fperson. By stark contrast, this has
OL,17,Faffected a huge amount of personnel -
OL,18,Fnot just my family, the hospital
OL,19,Fstaff, emergency services.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/20
