OL,3,CVictim of murder plot GP says he will
OL,4,C'never get over the anxiety and pain'
OL,6,F"He has brought the NHS into
OL,7,Fdisrepute. From my perspective he was
OL,8,Fin the ultimate position of trust.
OL,9,FCountless individuals each and every
OL,10,Fday place their trust in doctors to do
OL,11,Fthe right thing, to carry out their
OL,12,Fduties as per the training and the
OL,13,Foath that they they have undertaken.
OL,15,F"He has flagrantly abused his position
OL,16,Fof trust. I will never get over the
OL,17,Fanxiety and pain that he has caused me
OL,18,Fand my family."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/20
