OL,6,FThe court had previously heard that Mr
OL,7,FO'Hara had been in a relationship with
OL,8,FKwan's mother, Jenny Leung, for 21
OL,9,Fyears when he launched his attack.
OL,11,FShe had named Mr O'Hara in her will to
OL,12,Fthe effect that he could stay in her
OL,13,Fhouse in St Thomas Street, Newcastle,
OL,14,Fshould she die before her partner.
OL,16,FThat decision led to her having a
OL,17,Fstrained relationship with her son, so
OL,18,Fmuch so that the police were called
OL,19,Fwhen Kwan, a partner at Happy House
OL,20,FSurgery in Sunderland, burst into her
OL,21,Fhome uninvited in November 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/20
