OL,3,CVictim of murder plot GP says he will
OL,4,C'never get over the anxiety and pain'
OL,6,FA year later, Kwan, who is married
OL,7,Fwith a son and lived 50 miles south in
OL,8,FBrading Court, Ingleby Barwick,
OL,9,FTeesside, faked a letter from the NHS
OL,10,Fon his home computer to Mr O'Hara.
OL,12,FClaiming to be a community nurse
OL,13,Fcalled Raj Patel, he offered Mr O'Hara
OL,14,Fa home visit, following up that letter
OL,15,Fin January, the court was told.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/20
