OL,3,CVictim of murder plot GP says he will
OL,4,C'never get over the anxiety and pain'
OL,6,FIn the early hours of 22 January this
OL,7,Fyear, Kwan drove his car - using a
OL,8,Ffake registration plate - from his
OL,9,Ffamily home to a Premier Inn, in
OL,10,FNewcastle, where he had booked a room
OL,11,Funder a false name.
OL,13,FHe was captured on CCTV, shown to the
OL,14,Fcourt, leaving his room, wearing a
OL,15,Flong coat, hat, clinical mask and blue
OL,16,Fsurgical gloves.
OL,18,FFootage tracked the GP making his way
OL,19,Fon foot to the city centre home his
OL,20,Fmother shared with her partner of more
OL,21,Fthan 20 years.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/20
