OL,6,FMr O'Hara let the tinted-glasses-
OL,7,Fwearing GP into the house where he
OL,8,Fspent 45 minutes.
OL,10,FDuring this time, Kwan spoke in what
OL,11,Fthe court heard was broken English
OL,12,Fwith an Asian accent and told Mr
OL,13,FO'Hara he needed a covid booster.
OL,15,FHe took blood samples from Mr O'Hara,
OL,16,Fchecked the blood pressure of both him
OL,17,Fand Ms Leung, and then injected Mr
OL,18,FO'Hara's arm which caused him
OL,19,Fimmediate pain.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/20
