OL,4,C'never get over the anxiety and pain'
OL,6,FThe court was told earlier this month
OL,7,Fthat Mr O'Hara was suffering from
OL,8,FNecrotising Fasciitis - a rare and
OL,9,Flife-threatening, flesh-eating disease.
OL,11,FMr O'Hara said: "In order to cure this
OL,12,Fdisease, I underwent three separate
OL,13,Foperations which required surgeons to
OL,14,Fcut away large parts of my left arm to
OL,15,Fensure that all signs of the disease
OL,16,Fhad been removed so that it wouldn't
OL,17,Fcontinue to spread.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/20
