OL,6,FTwo weeks after the attack, Kwan was
OL,7,Farrested by police who found a haul of
OL,8,Fchemicals and associated equipment in
OL,9,Fhis detached garage.
OL,11,FAmong the array of chemicals was
OL,12,Farsenic and liquid mercury as well as
OL,13,Fcastor beans which can be used to make
OL,14,Fthe chemical weapon ricin.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G13/20
