OL,6,FPolice found a recipe for ricin on his
OL,7,Fcomputer but Ministry of Defence
OL,8,Fpoisons expert Professor Steven
OL,9,FEmmett, although still not sure which
OL,10,Fpoison was used, thought iodomethane
OL,11,Fwhich is commonly used in pesticides,
OL,12,Fwas more likely.
OL,14,FA search of his home also revealed a
OL,15,Fmobile phone used to text Mr O'Hara
OL,16,Fand storage devices containing
OL,17,Fresearch materials on poisons,
OL,18,Fguidance on murder investigations, and
OL,19,Ftoxicology books including a book
OL,20,Fcalled '10 poisons used to kill
OL,21,Fpeople'.
