OL,6,FContinuing his victim impact
OL,7,Fstatement, Mr O'Hara revealed he is no
OL,8,Flonger in a relationship with Kwan's
OL,9,Fmother and has moved out of the home
OL,10,Fthey shared.
OL,12,FHe said he was now living with his
OL,13,Fdaughter and her family and commended
OL,14,Fhis ex-wife Theresa for the loving
OL,15,Fsupport she has given him.
OL,17,FDespite moving on, the victim said he
OL,18,Fnow feared for his and his family's
OL,19,Ffuture.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G15/20
