OL,3,CVictim of murder plot GP says he will
OL,4,C'never get over the anxiety and pain'
OL,6,F"I feel incredibly guilty and fearful
OL,7,Fthat someday Thomas will be released
OL,8,Ffrom prison and I am petrified that he
OL,9,Fwill cause harm to my loved ones as a
OL,10,Fresult of me assisting the police in
OL,11,Fhis prosecution."
OL,13,FPaul Greaney KC, defending Kwan, told
OL,14,Fthe court there were "mixed motives"
OL,15,Fbehind the attempted murder.
