OL,6,FMr Greaney said: "This terrible scheme
OL,7,Fdid not have as its sole focus
OL,8,Ffinancial gain but was much more
OL,9,Fgenerally influenced by his feelings
OL,10,Fabout his relationship with his mother
OL,11,Fand the way she had treated him.
OL,13,F"It's not just financial gain, other
OL,14,Fthings are happening."
OL,16,FMr Greaney added: "There is little to
OL,17,Fextenuate offending as grave as this.
