OL,6,F"He is entitled to ask you to take
OL,7,Finto account the fact he, at the age
OL,8,Fof 53, has no previous convictions,
OL,9,Fthe fact he is a local GP and he
OL,10,Fshould be regarded as having been of
OL,11,Fpositive good character and thirdly it
OL,12,Fis plain he is not going to have an
OL,13,Feasy time in prison."
OL,15,FMr Greaney said probation officials
OL,16,Fhave assessed Kwan to pose a "medium
