OL,6,FProsecutors have applied for Kwan to
OL,7,Fbe ordered to pay more than #25,000 in
OL,8,Fcourt costs, which will be decided at
OL,9,Fa later date.
OL,11,FMrs Justice Lambert indicated on
OL,12,FThursday that the sentencing
OL,13,Fguidelines point towards a jail term
OL,14,Fin the range of 25 to 35 years, and Mr
OL,15,FMakepeace said aggravating factors
OL,16,Fpush the case to the top end of that.
OL,18,FMrs Justice Lambert suggested she
OL,19,Fmight give Kwan a 5% reduction in his
OL,20,Fsentence because he pleaded guilty
OL,21,Fafter the trial began.
